Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能把想做的事情告訴我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要洋裝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃很多吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和爸爸媽媽見面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇伊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真了不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太強大了 更本沒有打得必要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是變革者的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按捺不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅!? 首都全域!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在和蘇伊爾國王會談的同志們也被捲進去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬哈爾支部長他…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦使用核武器了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是空中的大功率激光攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星兵器…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memento-Mori 取得了預想之上的戰果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了這個力量的話 就能輕鬆滅掉反政府勢力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現實的角度 消滅了世界上的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:27.41,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a}拉格朗日3 資源衛星群
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser到達TRANS-AM極限時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我看到了大佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越理論極限的性能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 TWIN-DRIVE遠遠超乎我們的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是不得了的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是00 Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變世界的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞 你身體情況的數據我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今怎麼能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正保守一點多盡一份力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐 觀測系統探查到地球圈內有異常熱源反應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立刻到艦橋來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…衛星兵器…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能借用了太陽光發電系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然得到的情報還很少…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向哪裡開的火?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中東 蘇伊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇伊爾?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是A-LAWS…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 裡本斯·阿爾馬克的做法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修補完成後 托勒密出航
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開聯邦衛星兵器的破壞任務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到各自的崗位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 有些話要對大家說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一群人背地裡操縱聯邦 妄圖支配世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配世界?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼知道的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他們見過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的名字是「變革者」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用太陽光發電 從衛星軌道上進行的激光攻擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的攻擊範圍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的宇宙部隊已經開始破壞衛星兵器的行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成兩個艦隊同時攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥艦23艘 MS 43架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是宇宙部隊的全部戰力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 衛星兵器周邊A-LAWS正張網以待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這個戰力能不能行還…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池田 天行者方面的聯絡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止還沒有聯繫上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON不得不孤軍奮戰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由維塔孕育的生物終端 變革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫傢伙操縱著A-LAWS 並且掌握著維塔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話 在我們開始武力介入的5年前就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始活動了 是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崔尼蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓3架Gundam Throne參加武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有將搭載擬GN DRIVE的30架GN-X提供給聯合國 都是他們幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說他們改變了伊奧利亞的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣 洛克昂和克麗絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼重大的事情到現在才告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們號稱在執行伊奧利亞·肖漢博格的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是事實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方才很有可能是異端…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS製造的反政府勢力的虐殺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種做法怎麼可能會得到真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒A-LAWS 驅逐變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我自身的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加入 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 我和他們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致的情況我們都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在最要緊的是破壞敵方衛星兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·諾莉艾卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我們的夥伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們能做的 只有祈禱宇宙艦隊作戰成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和在阿扎帝斯坦的時候沒任何變化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐打算捨棄天行者 加入變革者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的思考方式是不會迎來真正的變革的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說你並非如自己所想那般特別
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和殺死哥哥們的傢伙聯手的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離拉格朗日3的小行星區域還有3266
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 要如何去找他們的基地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個任務請交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼對策嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勒維准尉 身體如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張照片…是您的夫人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 直到2個月前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被捲入了KATARON的反聯邦恐怖行動 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gadessa　Garazzo出動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪奈金大佐想出了個有趣的作戰方案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為人類 已經很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和提艾利亞的機體好像也有新裝備追加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是琳達的得意之作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期待戰果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser也能出擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為到Ptolemaeus的搬運過程 以及和00 TRANS-AM的配合實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在需要進行調整作業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就要分別了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有些話想和你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我不會離開的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為受到伊恩的推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將要成為Ptolemaeus的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 能收到回應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪來的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是找我的…誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到敵方基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向艦隊傳送可視加密通信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多 該去艦橋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點緊張嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是吧 稍微有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 補給情況怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0032結束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向托勒密乘員以外全體人員傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密在0032出航
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業員在補給完成之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將本基地廢棄 各種數據刪除之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請乘運輸艇 通過Y45路線脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密在0037時 開始執行破壞聯邦衛星兵器任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當心點啊 米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在托勒密?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:11:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想自己也有些能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用戰鬥也能做到的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵襲!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去第2格納庫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從三個方向 朝本基地的導彈攻擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的戰力多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法解析
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敵艦逃出同時 轉入任務計劃SA77
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點向第3格納庫移動!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運輸艇按順序進發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請動作快!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位 請坐在那邊的座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各機 發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐 托勒密號的操作拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就能專心炮擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中止補給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密緊急發射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把敵人引到我們身上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明… 明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補給作業中止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密固定用機械臂解除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各機 已發射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  0 Raiser的狀況怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要再花些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞 將運輸艇護衛到安全領域為止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios 進入防禦行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地被…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力場 展開的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閘門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各連接機械臂切斷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ptolemaeus 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦 出現!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4架Gundam也出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉入任務計劃SA77
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍部隊出現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總數12架的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮蔽了熱源…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 去迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和預測的一樣哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍部隊 接近!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:14:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TWINBUSTER-CANNON 高濃度壓縮粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型機竟然!
